experiences:
I have a consolidated experience in:
- Preparation of the statutory and consolidated financial statements of the Group  accordance;
- Management audit of IML Group business units (BU) (industrial and marine engine sales, construction of cogeneration and emergency plants, service & maintenance);
- Analysis of the profitability of each division and sharing of the corrective actions to be taken with the CEOs of the two BUs;
- Management of extraordinary transactions, such as acquisitions and company evaluations;
- Support to lawyers during the extrajudicial stage in the analysis and management of disputes, intended as the issue of injunctions aimed at recovering credits and the preparation of the ecessary documentation for the suits;
