- Maintaining relationships with credit and factoring institutions;
- Analysis and management of risks object of insurance coverage, negotiation of premiums and of the coverage with the insurance broker;
- Support to BU departments for the recovery of credits, preparation of the statistics on the outstanding and letters of notice;
