- Administrative management of personnel issues, such as recruitments, terminations and preparation of warning letters;
- Maintaining relationships with trade union;
- Maintaining relationships with contractual institutions;
- Opening and management of temporary layoffs during periods of company difficulties;
- Organization of training courses;
- Key user in the transition from Oracle to SAP system;

